-independent suppression\nfactor of $1/2$, away from the resonant region, even for small vacuum mixing\nangles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 1996 20:43:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Jul 1996 21:57:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 18 Aug 1996 03:00:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-17"}
